Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:23.54,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Aký sebecký hlupák.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:29.94,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriem na vás.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:34.94,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriem na vás!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:45.94,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Musím isť.
