Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:07.04,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Kontakt s Album potvrdený.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:07.94,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozkaz.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:12.94,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Pokračujte v monitorovaní.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:17.44,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Tentoraz nám neujdeš.
