Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:39.74,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Pomyslela som si, že aká prekrásna planéta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:53.34,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Zmenilo ti to život?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:58.34,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím, že áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:18.34,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Do riti!
